All Implemented Interfaces:
ExtensionInfo
public class JL5OutputExtensionInfo
extends JL5ExtensionInfo
A simple example of the output extension pattern. This extension uses a parent extension to set its options and expects all jobs to be enqueued directly in its scheduler by an ExtensionRewriter. It also provides a subclass of JLScheduler that performs an empty pass for the Parsed goal, since no files are actually parsed.
